---
title: Greek Goddess Salmon & Bulgur Bowls with Roasted Chickpeas, Harissa Hummus & Cucumber Feta Salad
description: This Greek-inspired grain-bowl stars roasted chickpeas and onions, a refreshing tomato-cucumber salad, tangy Greek vinaigrette, and salty feta cheese over bulgur—a hearty-yet-fluffy whole grain and longtime staple of both Middle Eastern and Mediterranean cuisines. Adding a final flourish are smoky, harissa-infused hummus and chopped dill, completing this un-bowl-ievable meal.
